sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Envoy as Envoy Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant BBR as Payload Processing BBR<br/>9004/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant MPR as model-provider-resolver<br/>plugin
    participant AT as api-translation<br/>plugin
    participant AKI as apikey-injection<br/>plugin
    participant NeMo as NeMo Guardrails<br/>(optional)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Provider as External AI Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 1: External Model Inference Request Processing

    Client->>Envoy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)<br/>Body: OpenAI Chat Completions format

    Note over Envoy,BBR: ext_proc filter intercepts request
    Envoy->>BBR: gRPC ext_proc RequestBody<br/>mTLS (Istio mesh)

    Note over BBR: Plugin 1: body-field-to-header<br/>Extracts "model" field → X-Gateway-Model-Name header

    BBR->>MPR: Execute RequestProcessor
    Note over MPR,K8s: Uses in-memory cache<br/>(controller-runtime watch)
    MPR-->>BBR: CycleState: {provider, model,<br/>credential-ref-name, credential-ref-namespace}

    BBR->>AT: Execute RequestProcessor
    Note over AT: Reads provider from CycleState<br/>Translates body to provider format<br/>(Anthropic: full translation,<br/>Azure/OpenAI/Vertex/Bedrock: path rewrite)
    AT-->>BBR: Mutated request body + headers

    BBR->>AKI: Execute RequestProcessor
    Note over AKI,K8s: Reads credential-ref from CycleState<br/>Looks up Secret in in-memory store
    AKI-->>BBR: Injected auth header<br/>(Authorization/x-api-key/api-key)

    opt NeMo Guardrails Enabled
        BBR->>NeMo: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP, configurable timeout (360s)
        NeMo-->>BBR: HTTP 200 {status: "success" | "blocked"}
        Note over BBR: If blocked → 403 Forbidden<br/>Short-circuits pipeline
    end

    BBR-->>Envoy: gRPC ext_proc response<br/>Mutated headers + body

    Envoy->>Provider: POST (provider-specific path)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Provider API key header

    Provider-->>Envoy: Provider-native response

    Note over Envoy,BBR: ext_proc filter intercepts response
    Envoy->>BBR: gRPC ext_proc ResponseBody<br/>mTLS (Istio mesh)

    BBR->>AT: Execute ResponseProcessor
    Note over AT: Translates provider response<br/>back to OpenAI format<br/>(Anthropic: full translation,<br/>Azure: field stripping)
    AT-->>BBR: Normalized OpenAI response body

    BBR-->>Envoy: gRPC ext_proc response<br/>Translated response body

    Envoy-->>Client: OpenAI Chat Completions response<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 2: Background Reconciliation (continuous)

    K8s-->>MPR: Watch ExternalModel CRDs<br/>(maas.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1)
    Note over MPR: Updates in-memory model store<br/>Maps model name → provider metadata

    K8s-->>AKI: Watch Secrets<br/>(label: inference.networking.k8s.io/bbr-managed=true)
    Note over AKI: Updates in-memory credential store<br/>Maps namespace/name → credential data
